desc:7R Spectrum Analyser
Author: 7thResonance
version: 1.3
about: modded version of the cockos spectrum analyser.
    - Added Sides graph (red)
    - Main (sum) graph is blue
    - RMS mode
    - ITU-R 468 weighting mode
changelog: added RMS mode

